<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Rainn Skii</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-29 00:57:09</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok.. I have this sword. It looks great in your hand..<BR>
The Stats are great... but let me tell you something..<BR>
<BR>
THE SWORD IS A CURSE!<BR>
<BR>
TELL YOU WHY!<BR>
<BR>
1. This sword has an AE proc that does 56 damage 3 times.<BR>
BUT! Did anyone tell you that this AE also hurts the person<BR>
who uses the sword? Ahhh! THAT REALLY SUCKS! If you have<BR>
alot of dex, you will hurt yourself ALOT in a long fight. <BR>
This is even worse when the mob resists your proc, but you<BR>
are still taking 165 damage everytime. Hehe you cant solo<BR>
with this thing, expect to loose.<BR>
<BR>
2. This sword will lag out 1/2 your party. The proc is <BR>
so stronge on this weapon that 1/2 your party gets lag spikes.<BR>
Not good in a serious fight. <BR>
<BR>
3. You will also find yourself switching weapons when you<BR>
have it. Because in any good dungeon you will always be<BR>
fighting many mobs at once, and enchanters spells are useless<BR>
if someone has this weapon. If you dont have an enchanter you <BR>
will find that all the mobs will be on you due to the strong<BR>
AE effect. <BR>
<BR>
4. If you have it. Get rid of it now. I have it, and I cant<BR>
get a ykesha for it these days. Everyone knows that this sword<BR>
is nothing but a curse. This is about the worst High level<BR>
sword in the game. They should really nerf the AE swords. There<BR>
gay and no one that knows this game uses them.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
So.. dont waste your time or energy on this one. Only way<BR>
this sword is good is if you are low level and it doesnt proc<BR>
yet. Other then that, dump this trash and get a good old<BR>
ykesha or some other good procing weapon.<BR>
<BR>
Rainn Skii<BR>
Level 50 Warrior<BR>
Innoruuk<BR>
