<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This blade is dropped in sebilis off a wandering mob on the dead side. The mob is lvl 55-56, and is an extremely rare spawn.<BR>
<BR>
The sword is not good to use with an enchanter, but the proc hitting you isnt too bad. Its easily combated with fire resist. My resist was only 39 and I was getting hit for about 35 a wave, I buffed it up to 79 and only got hit for about 17 a wave. Its not THAT bad. But with the AoE it pisses off alot of enchanters =<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
A_Rook<BR>
52nd warrior<BR>
Solusek Ro</font></td></tr></table>
