<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Gergely</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-18 03:01:23</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I used this sword and loved the taunt factor it had.  Very fast and the proc got the mobs attention.  The rumors that it cant be used with enchanters is false i didnt break mez one time while in sebilis after looting it or while in fear.  I really was hoping to use it against vox but i traded it recently so i wont get the chance.  For all of those who dont like this weapon give it to a low level twink and they will worship you.  Now is this the greatest weapon, definely not, but I liked it and had fun with it.  Besides looking great there is something great about dealing 900 dmg to a mob off from proc.  All my friends would kid me about being kamikazi warrior, but i made sure i used my froglock crown and got a good fire resistence buff in addition to my normal magic resistence buff and i proceeded to have the most fun i have ever had with any weapon =).  Even better trading it allowed my enchanter friend to get a very rare item that will him alive much longer.  Good hunting all.<BR>
Gergely</font></td></tr></table>
